verbose_text: In accordance with our previous data that the endogenous levels of IFITM3 do not change during senescence (XREF_FIG C), we did not observe any changes in the expression levels of a number of markers of senescence by immunoblot or qPCR (data not shown) upon the ectopic expression of IFITM3 in normal HFFF2s (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY G) or changes in the release of a number of sEVs (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY H).
